            	<h2>如何定制跟单？</h2>
                <div class="det_c">
<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;line-height:18pt;margin:11.25pt 0cm;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:'ˎ̥','serif';color:#333333;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:ˎ̥;mso-hansi-font-family:ˎ̥;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;">、登录</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:'ˎ̥','serif';color:#333333;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;">玩彩网</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:ˎ̥;mso-hansi-font-family:ˎ̥;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;">网首页，在左侧的登陆框中选择"购买彩票"；</span></p>
<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;line-height:18pt;margin:11.25pt 0cm;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:'ˎ̥','serif';color:#333333;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:ˎ̥;mso-hansi-font-family:ˎ̥;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;">、在左侧的导航栏中选择您要定制自动跟单的彩种（以胜负彩为例）；</span></p>
<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;line-height:18pt;margin:11.25pt 0cm;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:'ˎ̥','serif';color:#333333;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:ˎ̥;mso-hansi-font-family:ˎ̥;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;">、在胜负彩页面选择"自动跟单"，若您有确定要跟单的用户，可直接在搜索框内搜索该超级红人；您也可以查看自动跟单定制列表；</span></p>
<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;line-height:18pt;margin:11.25pt 0cm;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:'ˎ̥','serif';color:#333333;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:ˎ̥;mso-hansi-font-family:ˎ̥;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;">、在自动跟单定制列表中，您可以选择您要定制的超级红人，已满额发起人无法定制；您还可以选择您要定制的玩法；点击"定制"进入定制该发起人页面；</span></p>
<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;line-height:18pt;margin:11.25pt 0cm;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:'ˎ̥','serif';color:#333333;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:ˎ̥;mso-hansi-font-family:ˎ̥;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;">、在定制跟单页面，填写"每期认购金额"，确认无误后，点击"立即定制"即定制成功。</span></p>
<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:left;line-height:18pt;margin:11.25pt 0cm;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:'ˎ̥','serif';color:#333333;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;"></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:ˎ̥;mso-hansi-font-family:ˎ̥;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;">您可以在"我的账户"下的"定制跟单"中查看您的自动跟单记录，并可随时对其进行编辑或取消。</span></p>

